{"lemma":"لَجِبَةٍ","slug":"لَجِبَةٍ","root":"ل.ج.ب","root_slug":"ل-ج-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-ج-ب","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37573","n37574","n37575","n37576","n37578","n37577"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37573","headword_ar":"لَجْبَةٌ","root":"ljb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lujobapN","text_ar":"لُجْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lijobapN","text_ar":"لِجْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajabapN","text_ar":"لَجَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[but see what is said respecting the last of the pls. mentioned below] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajibapN","text_ar":"لَجِبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lijabapN","text_ar":"لِجَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) the last two from Th. (TA.) A sheep or goat ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$Ap","text_ar":"شاة"},{"kind":"text","text":", K), or a sheep only, not a goat, (ISk, S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which the milk has become little in quantity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or a sheep or goat ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$Ap","text_ar":"شاة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which has passed four months since her bringing forth, and of which the milk has in consequence dried up:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S:) or it is an epithet applied specially to a goat: (K:) a poet (Muhelhil, TA,) says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"Eajibato A^abonaAw^unaA mino fiEolinaA\n                      \n                     \n                        A_i*o nabiyEu Alxayola biAlmiEozaY All~ijaAbo"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Our sons wondered at our action, in our selling horses for goats of which the milk had become little,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dried up"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) and contr.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abounding with milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) a poet applies the two epithets"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajobap","text_ar":"لَجْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaA$ikap","text_ar":"حَاشِكَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"to the same sheep or goat; but he may mean that her milk was little at one time, and abundant at another. (TA.) Pl. [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajobapN","text_ar":"لَجْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lijaAbN","text_ar":"لِجَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajobaAtN","text_ar":"لَجْبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(this being allowed by Mbr, agreeably with analogy, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajabaAtN","text_ar":"لَجَبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K): the last dev. with respect to rule; for by rule it should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajobaAtN","text_ar":"لَجْبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; unless it be originally a subst. used as an epithet, like as one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_imoraA^apN kalobapN","text_ar":"اـِمْرَاَةٌ كَلْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or unless ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajabapN","text_ar":"لَجَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"be a syn. of the sing. (S.) Sb says, that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajabaAtN","text_ar":"لَجَبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used as pl. because some of the Arabs used ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajabapN","text_ar":"لَجَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as sing. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~jb","text_ar":"اللّجب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~ajabu","text_ar":"اللَّجَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a quasi-pl. n.,], occurring in the following words of a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fayaboduw A^amovaAlu Alljbi mina Al*~ahabi","text_ar":"فَيَبْدُو اَمْثَالُ اللجبِ مِنَ الذَّهَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is said to be pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajobapN","text_ar":"لَجْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~ijabu","text_ar":"اللِّجَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiSaEN","text_ar":"قِصَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSoEapN","text_ar":"قَصْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  In a trad. respecting Ed-Dejjál, according to one reading, occur the words,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bljbtY AlbAbi","text_ar":"بلجبتى البابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but Aboo-Moosà says, that the right reading is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"f","text_ar":"ف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[instead of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":", and with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"before it: i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bilajiyfataY AlbAb","text_ar":"بِلَجِيفَتَى الباب"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ljf","text_ar":"لجف"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","ISk","As"]},{"entry_id":"n37574","headword_ar":"لُجْبَةٌ","root":"ljb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajobapN","text_ar":"لَجْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n37575","headword_ar":"لِجْبَةٌ","root":"ljb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajobapN","text_ar":"لَجْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n37576","headword_ar":"لَجَبَةٌ","root":"ljb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajobapN","text_ar":"لَجْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n37578","headword_ar":"لَجَبَةٌ","root":"ljb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajobapN","text_ar":"لَجْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n37577","headword_ar":"لَجِبَةٌ","root":"ljb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lajobapN","text_ar":"لَجْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}